headline: Molina Healthcare (MOH) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of healthcare insurance company Molina Healthcare (NYSE:MOH) jumped 2.2% in the afternoon session after the stock appeared to rebound from recent lows despite the publication of bearish commentary.

headline: Molina Healthcare Draws a Major Bet From Cobalt Capital After a Sharp Pullback
summary: Molina Healthcare is trading near multi-year lows, yet Cobalt Capital moved in with a position large enough to make MOH a top-four holding. For shareholders trying to understand whether this downturn represents structural erosion or cyclical noise, this move offers a revealing clue.
